column5: Out on the Main Lake Basin This AM..  We were determined to Find some Great Whites, The Fifth Move paid off,  The Ice Rod Spiel made for me Was The "Best"  Worked as advertised Plus!!!            Thanks Chris    Rick
Glad you found them Rick...  Did you tell them to be ready for another visit ....soon  Cheers, Ice Fisherman
Yes  I sent this Guy Back down!!!!  Told Him He had to wait for the"Ice Fisherman"       Rick
nice going rick we have been finding them out in the main basin too  rod looks great
I always thought lures caught fish?  Great report and nice rod.
Sweet reward for your efforts Rick    Great looking whites I'm kind of wondering how I can get my hands on one of them Spiel's special ice rod      I hear they're the greatest    ;) Leechman
Sheeeesh, they don't look like Lakers Rick but I'm pleased your enjoying the rod.    They're not so hard to get Jacques, I'm taking orders for next years ice season.
Chris  No Lakers on The "Rod" To-day  But the season is not over!!!   Rick
You found them! nice looking size. did you paint a big white X on the spot for me, so i know where to go?
Good going Rick.  Nice fish and really nice rod  Joey

Just teasing you Rick, you asked for a trout rod and you're catching whities, don't get me wrong, I love whities. I'm just looking forward to the report where your new rod puts a hurt'n on some big lakers.
Nice big whities Rick. WTG keepin' moving till you find 'em. We had to move lots the last time out for whities too, i find its hard to drag myself off to another spot when its really cold.
Chris  I did get a Laker but I was not using the New Rod.  I will get you that Pic before the season ends.
